title: Watch Frank Ocean Talk Blonde In Unearthed Interview
text: Frank Ocean interviews are like unicorns, so it's a big deal every time one pops up. And today, as Pitchfork points out, the Frank Ocean fan page TeamFrankDaily has unearthed interview footage from who knows where of Frank discussing the making of Blonde.
